just what a computation

00:03:20.950 --> 00:03:25.060
is, what the limits are, what
the power of a single process

00:03:25.060 --> 00:03:25.630
is.

00:03:25.630 --> 00:03:28.060
Then it proceeds to
the question of what it

00:03:28.060 --> 00:03:31.150
means when processes interact.

00:03:31.150 --> 00:03:34.630
But for both single and
interacting processes,

00:03:34.630 --> 00:03:39.260
the assumption is that nothing
in the world is going wrong.

00:03:39.260 --> 00:03:42.430
The processes themselves
might have some problems,

00:03:42.430 --> 00:03:46.030
but there's nothing about their
environment that's problematic.

00:03:46.030 --> 00:03:49.040
